                    <p class="faq-expanded__lead">Get answers about object clause definition, resolution, ultra vires, MGT-14, NIC codes, timelines, and retroactive changes for Mumbai companies.</p>
                    @include('partials.faq-enquiry-form', ['enquiryLocation' => 'Mumbai', 'enquiryService' => 'Change in Object Clause in Mumbai'])
