                <p><strong>Ultra vires kya hota hai?</strong> Agar company apne object clause ke bahar koi business activity kare, toh woh ultra vires hai &ndash; matlab illegal aur void. Contracts enforceable nahi honge. Directors personally liable ho sakte hain. Object clause turant amend karo.</p>
